org.dice_research.squirrel.collect

Class SqlBasedUriCollector

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dice_research.squirrel.collect.SqlBasedUriCollector
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, UriCollector, org.dice_research.squirrel.sink.SinkBase

    @NotThreadSafe
public class SqlBasedUriCollector
extends Object
implements UriCollector, Closeable
    An implementation of the UriCollector interface that is backed by a SQL database.
    Author:
    Geralod Souza Junior (gsjunior@mail.uni-paderborn.de), Michael Röder (michael.roeder@uni-paderborn.de) NotThreadSafe because the prepared statement objects used internally are not stateless.

      • getTableName

        protected static String getTableName(org.dice_research.squirrel.data.uri.CrawleableUri uri)
        Retrieves the URIs table name from its properties or generates a new table name and adds it to the URI (using the "URI_COLLECTOR_TABLE_NAME" property).
        Parameters:
        uri - the URI for which a table name is needed.
        Returns:
        the table name of the URI

      • generateTableName

        protected static String generateTableName(String uri)
        Generates a table name based on the given URI. Only alphanumeric characters of the URI are kept. If the URI exceeds the length of MAX_ALPHANUM_PART_OF_TABLE_NAME=30 the exceeding part is cut off. After that the hash value of the original URI is appended.
        Parameters:
        uri - the URI for which a table name has to be generated
        Returns:
        the table name of the URI
